To install:
- Download temurin jdk (https://adoptium.net/en-GB/temurin/releases at the time of this writing) to project dir
- Download scala cli (https://github.com/VirtusLab/scala-cli/releases at the time of this writing) to project dir
- Run launch.bat to install in local env [

@echo off
:: Set the path to your specific JVM folder
set "JAVA_HOME=%~dp0jvm\jdk-25.0.1+8"

:: Add our local bin and local java to the temporary PATH
set "PATH=%~dp0bin;%JAVA_HOME%\bin;%PATH%"

echo ---------------------------------------
echo Scala Portable Environment Loaded!
echo ---------------------------------------
echo Java Home: %JAVA_HOME%
echo.
:: Verify Java is found
java -version
echo.
:: Verify Scala-CLI is found
scala-cli --version
echo ---------------------------------------
cmd /k

]

- To build: scala-cli --power package projects/web_app/app.sc --assembly -o app.jar --force
- To run: java -jar app.jar --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8080 
